Author: grumpygrumbles
Text: yep my mom literally sat down next to me and was like “I only eat good stuff but today my whole plate is bad stuff” when she sat down next to me with exactly the same plate - except I was on seconds and borderline binge-mode because I fasted for 2 days out of anxiety for that one meal  f u c k this holiday and all the diet-talk that comes with it.
